Collections.rule:
Individual: @L*
	Types: Team
	Facts: Location @K*,
		playedAs @L* (mm:hashEncode)

Individual: @B*
	Types: Game
	Facts: hasHomeTeam @L*,
	          hasAwayTeam @H*

Individual: @H* (mm:hashEncode)
	Types: GamePlayer
	Facts: isTeam @H*,
		isAwayTeamOf @B*

Individual: @L* (mm:hashEncode)
	Types: GamePlayer
	Facts: isTeam @L*,
		isHomeTeamOf @B*,
		FoulsComitted @BF* (xsd:integer),
		FoulsDrawn @BN* (xsd:integer),
		Rebounds @AP* (xsd:integer),
		Assists @AR* (xsd:integer),
		Points @AT* (xsd:integer),
		Turnovers @AV* (xsd:integer)

Individual: @H*
	Types: Team
	Facts: Location @G*,
		playedAs @H* (mm:hashEncode)
